{"id": 1, "name": "Texte de la commission  sur la proposition de loi, adopt\u00e9e par le S\u00e9nat, apr\u00e8s engagement de la proc\u00e9dure acc\u00e9l\u00e9r\u00e9e, visant \u00e0 sortir la France du pi\u00e8ge du narcotrafic (n\u00b0907)., n\u00b0\u00a01043-A0 rectifi\u00e9", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/1043/AN/1", "date": "2025-03-11", "status": "Non soutenu", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "Paul", "last_name": "Molac", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Jean-Pierre", "last_name": "Bataille", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Salvatore", "last_name": "Castiglione", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Paul-Andr\u00e9", "last_name": "Colombani", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Charles", "last_name": "de Courson", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Max", "last_name": "Mathiasin", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Yannick", "last_name": "Favennec-B\u00e9cot", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Martine", "last_name": "Froger", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "St\u00e9phane", "last_name": "Lenormand", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Laurent", "last_name": "Mazaury", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Laurent", "last_name": "Panifous", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}, {"first_name": "Nicole", "last_name": "Sanquer", "party": "Libert\u00e9s, Ind\u00e9pendants, Outre-mer et Territoires"}], "summary": "Cet amendement vise \u00e0 mieux calibrer l\u2019infraction d\u2019intrusion dans le \u00ab\u00a0domaine affect\u00e9\u00a0\u00bb \u00e0 un \u00e9tablissement p\u00e9nitentiaire. Ce domaine n\u2019est pas\u00a0clairement d\u00e9fini et pourrait donc recouvrir les abords imm\u00e9diats et la voie publique. Il est donc n\u00e9cessaire de pr\u00e9ciser que l\u2019infraction ne pourra\u00a0\u00eatre caract\u00e9ris\u00e9e qu\u2019en cas de volont\u00e9\u00a0de troubler l\u2019ordre ou la tranquillit\u00e9\u00a0de l\u2019\u00e9tablissement. La r\u00e9daction propos\u00e9e par cet amendement s\u2019inspire de celle pr\u00e9vue en mati\u00e8re d\u2019intrusion dans l\u2019enceinte d\u2019un \u00e9tablissement scolaire (article\u00a0431\u201122 du code p\u00e9nal)."}